ygData.subject: Re: New Quest
ygData.msgSnippet: Actually it s more then that.  It seems we bards have become the pony express of norrath.  Kelethin, Freeport, HighHold Keep, and Qeynos have become the mail
ygData.messageBody:
Actually it's more then that. It seems we bards have become
the "pony express" of norrath. Kelethin, Freeport, HighHold Keep,
and Qeynos have become the mail stops. There may be more but those were
the only ones I undertook last night. There did seem to be trouble with
the Feeport mail stop. I believe there are also two new quests in
Qeynos but I could be mistaken and merely never triggered them before.

Adon singer of the Glories of Veeshan
Bard of Povar
